<h2 id="what-is-mindbody">🏋️ What Is Mindbody?</h2>

<p>Mindbody is an all-in-one business management platform built for fitness studios, gyms, spas, salons, and wellness practitioners. Originally launched in 2001, it has grown into the dominant player in the wellness software space, serving over 60,000 businesses globally as of 2026.</p>

<p>The platform combines scheduling, point-of-sale, client management, marketing automation, staff management, and — critically — access to the Mindbody consumer marketplace. That marketplace is what separates Mindbody from most competitors: it's a discovery platform where millions of consumers search for and book fitness classes, spa appointments, and wellness services.</p>

<p>In 2026, Mindbody operates under the Mindbody + ClassPass umbrella following their 2021 merger, which has created both opportunities and complications for operators. The integration means ClassPass members can now book directly into your schedule — bringing incremental revenue but also raising questions about rate dilution and brand control.</p>

